You can create an override for the domain and set a value on 
frontier.queue-total-budget.

Note that if you are using the default frontier, the setting on a domain 
will apply separately to each subdomain. In other words if you set 
queue-total-budge=1000 on yahoo.com, then you could get up to 1000 urls 
from each of yahoo.com, www.yahoo.com, news.yahoo.com, 
foo.bar.baz.blah.yahoo.com etc.

